sketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is an issue for the Chinese Olympic Committee and the national federation will need to get involved,\\\" he added, referring to reports that Sutton had been accredited by the Chinese Committee.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chinese Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Sutton\", \"score\": 0.999999999984766, \"rank\": 1.4204395861891482e-11, \"text\": \"Sutton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Sutton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Sutton\"}, {\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9759506000301894, \"rank\": 0.021933937247609538, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking forward I can tell you we will obviously look into this issue.\\\"\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Coaches are not accredited by us but by the National Olympic Committees, and approved by the IOC,\\\" a World Triathlon spokesperson said on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9662878743944016, \"rank\": 0.034888283811687036, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committees\", \"types\": [\"Q4322