": 2267, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde walked off waving to crowd, seeking out the orange-clad Dutch fans who were applauding among the others sending boos his way.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.8222135342638189, \"rank\": 0.16001407051627842, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC had already defended the Dutch Olympic Committee's decision to bring Van de Velde to the Games and on Sunday Adams added: \\\"This is an issue that was discussed with the National Olympic Committee and they assured us there were many safeguarding measures.\\\"\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.823708864414694e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6029994113226556e-17, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999963024493, \"rank\": 3.695489105630201e-09, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, foll